*.swp

# npm artifacts (used by examples/express-app — see its README for the
# `npm install` setup step). Lockfile is also gitignored: pinning is
# the user's choice and the example's `package.json` only declares a
# semver range against a single dep.
**/node_modules/
package-lock.json
# docs/ is generated/working notes — gitignored. We carve out only
# the WIT manifest tree (consumed by the abi_parity drift gate test
# in CI). Everything else under docs/ stays out of git.
docs/**
!docs/wit/
!docs/wit/**